Internal node is needed for KIS.

I'm not sure if the "Placeholder" internal still exist in 1.0, but you can try this MM patch : 

    @PART[*]:HAS[#CrewCapacity[*],!INTERNAL[]]:FINAL{  INTERNAL{  name = Placeholder}}

